{"tid":2492290,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯爾 再為公義發聲","createTime":"2021-04-17T04:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T04:52:42.000Z","uid":177873,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a1615aa95bc819da542e08b45b5e5ebf685e5f68","tid":2492290,"uid":177873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"目前效力費倫巴治的土耳其裔德國球星奧斯爾，去年就曾經在Twitter發表批評中國政府打壓維吾爾族人的言論，被中國傳媒封殺至今。周五這位德國中場再次於Twitter上就着羅興亞人於緬甸被打壓一事發聲，贏得不少網民留言支持。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近於緬甸國內發生的反政變示威，緬甸軍警連日來的濫捕、毆打以及濫殺無辜的消息一直都被國際傳媒廣泛報道，加上其實緬軍過去數年一直都有針對少數族裔人士，以不同的方式去壓迫、虐待以及殘殺羅興亞人以及其他少數民族，此前一直相當關注人權問題的奧斯爾，周五又再次於Twitter上發聲：「作為人類，我們需要站在一起，特別是面對好像緬甸這樣的國家。我不為那些現在並不安全的人祈禱，為我們的羅興亞兄弟姐妹祈禱，是時候發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXCfLKpQ6z12aiupb8pHrpQEpZaq32FzFYdmvymPAftXT?filename=eMDi1R1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMDi1R1.png&h=50f25b70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdQeLNTjG4eDKRsGS5NitF6Hq4JSHa7BkJdMXKw1tPeyN?filename=a8paSYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8paSYH.png&h=a73137e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210416/CPW4YDPRPVCDJFFOTT7JX4OXZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210416%2FCPW4YDPRPVCDJFFOTT7JX4OXZI%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=e321cd35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210416%2FCPW4YDPRPVCDJFFOTT7JX4OXZI%2F&h=e309ba79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210416/CPW4YDPRPVCDJFFOTT7JX4OXZI/</a>"},{"pid":"c9fd5f3ec1e9b8301e6ab81a1c322814e0523be4","tid":2492290,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40a70a6be3d664422c036a03f99f6022bf33e68","tid":2492290,"ui